verbose_text: Our previous studies reported that Zfat gene ablation in thymic T cells in Zfat f/f -LckCre mice induces a marked decrease in the number of cluster of differentiation (CD) 4 + CD8 + double positive (DP) cells, alongside impaired positive selection and excessive apoptosis.
